"486","<BODY STYLE=font: 10pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif>"
"487","<P STYLE=margin: 0>&nbsp;</P>"
"488","<P STYLE=margin: 0></P>"
"489","<P STYLE=font: 10pt AvenirNext LT Com Regular,sans-serif; margin: 0 2.3pt 0 0; text-align: center><B>Report of Independent Registered"
"490","Public Accounting Firm</B></P>"
"491","<P STYLE=font: 10pt AvenirNext LT Com Regular,sans-serif; margin: 0 2.3pt 0 0; text-align: center><B>&nbsp;</B></P>"
"492","<P STYLE=font: 10pt AvenirNext LT Com Regular,sans-serif; margin: 0 2.3pt 0 0>To the Board of Trustees and Shareholders of American"
"493","Funds Short-Term Tax-Exempt Bond Fund, Limited Term Tax-Exempt Bond Fund of America, The Tax-Exempt Bond Fund of America, American"
"494","High-Income Municipal Bond Fund, The Tax-Exempt Fund of California and American Funds Tax-Exempt Fund of New York</P>"
"495","<P STYLE=font: 10pt AvenirNext LT Com Regular,sans-serif; margin: 0 2.3pt 0 0>&nbsp;</P>"
"496","<P STYLE=font: 10pt AvenirNext LT Com Regular,sans-serif; margin: 0 2.3pt 0 0>In planning and performing our audits of the financial"
"497","statements of American Funds Short-Term Tax-Exempt Bond Fund, Limited Term Tax-Exempt Bond Fund of America, The Tax-Exempt Bond"
"498","Fund of America, American High-Income Municipal Bond Fund, The Tax-Exempt Fund of California and American Funds Tax-Exempt Fund"
"499","of New York (hereafter referred to as the &ldquo;Funds&rdquo;) as of and for the year ended July 31, 2015, in accordance with the"
"500","standards of the Public Company Accounting Oversight Board (United States), we considered the Funds&rsquo; internal control over"
"501","financial reporting, including controls over safeguarding securities, as a basis for designing our auditing procedures for the"
"502","purpose of expressing our opinion on the financial statements and to comply with the requirements of Form N-SAR, but not for the"
"503","purpose of expressing an opinion on the effectiveness of the Funds&rsquo; internal control over financial reporting. Accordingly,"
"504","we do not express an opinion on the effectiveness of the Funds&rsquo; internal control over financial reporting.</P>"
"505","<P STYLE=font: 10pt AvenirNext LT Com Regular,sans-serif; margin: 0 2.3pt 0 0>&nbsp;</P>"
"506","<P STYLE=font: 10pt AvenirNext LT Com Regular,sans-serif; margin: 0 2.3pt 0 0>The management of the Funds is responsible for"
"507","establishing and maintaining effective internal control over financial reporting. In fulfilling this responsibility, estimates"
"508","and judgments by management are required to assess the expected benefits and related costs of controls. A fund&rsquo;s internal"
"509","control over financial reporting is a process designed to provide reasonable assurance regarding the reliability of financial reporting"
"510","and the preparation of financial statements for external purposes in accordance with generally accepted accounting principles."
"511","A fund&rsquo;s internal control over financial reporting includes those policies and procedures that (1) pertain to the maintenance"
"512","of records that, in reasonable detail, accurately and fairly reflect the transactions and dispositions of the assets of the funds;"
"513","(2) provide reasonable assurance that transactions are recorded as necessary to permit preparation of financial statements in accordance"
"514","with generally accepted accounting principles, and that receipts and expenditures of the funds are being made only in accordance"
"515","with authorizations of management and trustees of the funds; and (3) provide reasonable assurance regarding prevention or timely"
"516","detection of unauthorized acquisition, use or disposition of a fund&rsquo;s assets that could have a material effect on the financial"
"517","statements.</P>"
"518","<P STYLE=font: 10pt AvenirNext LT Com Regular,sans-serif; margin: 0 2.3pt 0 0>&nbsp;</P>"
"519","<P STYLE=font: 10pt AvenirNext LT Com Regular,sans-serif; margin: 0 2.3pt 0 0>Because of its inherent limitations, internal control"
"520","over financial reporting may not prevent or detect misstatements. Also, projections of any evaluation of effectiveness to future"
"521","periods are subject to the risk that controls may become inadequate because of changes in conditions, or that the degree of compliance"
"522","with the policies or procedures may deteriorate.</P>"
"523","<P STYLE=font: 10pt AvenirNext LT Com Regular,sans-serif; margin: 0 2.3pt 0 0>&nbsp;</P>"
"524","<P STYLE=font: 10pt AvenirNext LT Com Regular,sans-serif; margin: 0 2.3pt 0 0>A deficiency in internal control over financial"
"525","reporting exists when the design or operation of a control does not allow management or employees, in the normal course of performing"
"526","their assigned functions, to prevent or detect misstatements on a timely basis. A material weakness is a deficiency, or a combination"
"527","of deficiencies, in internal control over financial reporting, such that there is a reasonable possibility that a material misstatement"
"528","of the Funds&rsquo; annual or interim financial statements will not be prevented or detected on a timely basis.</P>"
"529","<P STYLE=font: 10pt AvenirNext LT Com Regular,sans-serif; margin: 0 2.3pt 0 0>&nbsp;</P>"
"530","<P STYLE=font: 10pt AvenirNext LT Com Regular,sans-serif; margin: 0 2.3pt 0 0>Our consideration of the Funds&rsquo; internal"
"531","control over financial reporting was for the limited purpose described in the first paragraph and would not necessarily disclose"
"532","all deficiencies in internal control over financial reporting that might be material weaknesses under standards established by"
"533","the Public Company Accounting Oversight Board (United States). However, we noted no deficiencies in the Funds&rsquo; internal control"
"534","over financial reporting and its operation, including controls over safeguarding securities, that we consider to be material weaknesses"
"535","as defined above as of July 31, 2015.</P>"
"536","<P STYLE=font: 10pt AvenirNext LT Com Regular,sans-serif; margin: 0 2.3pt 0 0>&nbsp;</P>"
"537","<P STYLE=font: 10pt AvenirNext LT Com Regular,sans-serif; margin: 0 2.3pt 0 0>This report is intended solely for the information"
"538","and use of management and the Board of Trustees of American Funds Short-Term Tax-Exempt Bond Fund, Limited Term Tax-Exempt Bond"
"539","Fund of America, The Tax-Exempt Bond Fund of America, American High-Income Municipal Bond Fund, The Tax-Exempt Fund of California"
"540","and American Funds Tax-Exempt Fund of New York and the Securities and Exchange Commission and is not intended to be and should"
"541","not be used by anyone other than these specified parties.</P>"
